properties.Name: MineCostType
properties.Description:
A cost associated with a mine, activity, procedure, asset etc.

Ex:
- Lease operating costs
- Production
- Production tax
- Oil and gas depreciation
- Depletion
- Amortization
- Trucking
- Handling
- Railway Transport
- Labor
- Contracted Labor
- Equipment
- Material
- Port Handling
- Concentrate transport and handling
- General and administration
- Transportation
- Lease Operating 
- Operating 
- Finding
- Operating
- Maintenance

where:

Operating Costs - The sum of lease operating costs, production taxes, G&A expenses, and oil and gas depreciation, depletion, and amortization.

Finding Costs - The capital costs associated with finding and developing oil and gas reserves.
